revisions.description: Update DESCRIPTION clause of MODULE-IDENTITY and PRODUCT-RELEASE clause of AGENT-CAPABILITIES.

Added rbnNotifyEnhanceCap2 which include rbnNotifyEnhanceMIBObjectGroup. SNMP agent may append rbnNEGroupName to rbnNELinkUp and rbnNELinkDown notifications.
